      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! I\u2019ve treated this car like my absolute baby\u2014it\u2019s in stunning condition and still has that fresh feel inside and out. It\u2019s been garage-kept, super well-loved, and drives as smooth as the day it was first bought. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
