    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of analog engineering. This example features the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine, boasting individual throttle bodies and a high-compression ratio that delivers a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-Differential Lock for optimal lateral traction. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a documented VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The factory suspension maintains its original damping characteristics, providing the communicative feedback expected of a true M-car. The exterior paint retains original factory depth and luster, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear or UV-induced dash fatigue. Mechanically flawless and cosmetically pristine, this is a turnkey specimen for the serious collector.",
